Maintainer: David Cortes <david.cortes.rivera@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/david-cortes/approxcdf
BugReports: https://github.com/david-cortes/approxcdf/issues
Description: Fast approximations for the cumulative distribution function (CDF) of the
  multivariate normal (MVN) distribution, based on the two-variate bivariate screening (TVBS)
  method from Bhat (2018) <doi:10.1016/j.trb.2018.01.011> for five and higher dimensions
  with some small improvements such as employing the variable reordering technique from
  Gibson, Glasbey, Elton (1994) <doi:10.1142/9789814533751>, matrix regularization, and others;
  and based on the more exact methods from Plackett (1954) <doi:doi.org/10.2307/2332716>,
  Gassmann (2003) <doi:10.1198/1061860032283>, Drezner, Wesolowsky (1990) <doi:10.1080/00949659008811236>,
  Drezner (1994) <doi:10.1090/S0025-5718-1994-1185242-8>, Tsay, Ke (2021) <doi:10.1080/03610918.2021.1884718>,
  and Genz (2004) <doi:10.1023/B:STCO.0000035304.20635.31> for four and lower dimensions.
Suggests: testthat, mvtnorm
